<br />\n於我而言，國際線係將街頭及議會戰線戰果最大化嘅手段，但係從來都無話點先算成功<br />\n因為一日香港未重光，亦未算成功。<br />\n與其灰心失意，倒不如多作思考，付諸行動。<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"bce398faf388c6ac7d4b9ff4ef9de340640ba241","tid":2074724,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"今日局勢就算買曬所有大豆，都幫唔到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b7dcd8bac90e9fbdad4dd594698a5e36429333","tid":2074724,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:03:16.000Z","msg":"如果咁早就出手 未到11月選舉就打緊世界大戰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905f68d13f3fa3914bbd61f885cec7ea93fbd2c1","tid":2074724,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:12:50.000Z","msg":"trump的弱點是經濟$$<br />\n<br />\n支那睇穿了"},{"pid":"1f3fc0d638708b4e9a7deb29d4135f26716d8418","tid":2074724,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ba3233865e96e3851a4d1eca169f470f242679","tid":2074724,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"我地係咪應該買下biden唔好淨買一邊"},{"pid":"f41c990e58b6a7551fdb20b90c565797afb8b01b","tid":2074724,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"一步步黎啦<br />\n香港咁有影響力都未搞得掂 何況新疆<br />\n未做唔代表唔會做"}]}